ervices environment.<br /> <strong>What You’ll Bring</strong><br /> <strong>Required</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>1-3 years of experience in inside sales, business development, account management, or a related role</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Comfort with outbound but “warm” outreach (calls, emails, follow-ups)</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Experience using CRM (specific platforms are teachable)</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Strong communication, organization, follow-through and confidence</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Coachability, resilience, and comfort hearing “no”</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>Nice to Have</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>Exposure to B2B services or recurring revenue businesses</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Experience selling into operations, IT, or compliance teams</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Familiarity with prospecting tools like Apollo, ZoomInfo, or similar.</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>Why This Role Is Different</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span><strong>Not a call center role</strong> – quality conversations over volume dialing</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span><strong>Real ownership</strong> – you help close deals, not just set meetings</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span><strong>Career growth</strong> – opportunity to grow into senior sales, account management, or outside sales</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span><strong>Worklife balance</strong> – inside sales model with very limited travel</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>What You’ll Do</strong><br /> <strong>Generate New Revenue Opportunities</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>Follow-up activities to help facilitate deal closure and expansion opportunities</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Identify expansion opportunities within existing shredding customers and targeted prospects</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Conduct outbound (but warm) calls and emails each week to introduce ITAD, storage, and scanning solutions</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Qualify customer needs and propose practical, compliant solutions</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>Run a Clean, Measurable Sales Process</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>Track all activity, conversations, and deal stages in <strong>Insightly CRM</strong></span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Maintain accurate pipeline data for forecasting and reporting</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Move opportunities forward with clear next steps and follow-ups</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>Collaborate & Deliver for Customers</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>Partner closely with Customer Service and Operations to ensure smooth handoffs</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Participate in occasional local site visits or customer maintenance meetings</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Deliver professional proposals and solution summaries</span></span></p> </ul> <p><span><span><strong>How Success Is Measured</strong></span></span></p> <ul> <li> <p><span><span>Ability to create viable opportunities from warm leads</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Creating cross-sell opportunities from outreach to existing customers</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Regular follow-through to maximize opportunity close rate</span></span></p> <li> <p><span><span>Revenue growth from warm leads and cross-selling opportunities</span></span></p> </ul> <p> #zip</p> ]]>
