ganizational skills</p> </ul> <p><strong>Minimum Qualifications:</strong></p> <ul> <li> <p>1–3 years of relevant Physician Assistant experience preferred</p> <li> <p>Active New York State Physician Assistant license</p> <li> <p>National PA certification</p> <li> <p>DEA registration (or ability to obtain)</p> <li> <p>Intermediate proficiency in MS Office and electronic medical records (Epic preferred)</p> </ul> <p><strong>Preferred Skills:</strong></p> <ul> <li> <p>Strong clinical assessment and diagnostic abilities</p> <li> <p>Ability to manage and coordinate a diverse patient caseload</p> <li> <p>Experience working within collaborative practice agreements</p> <li> <p>Excellent interpersonal, communication, and leadership skills</p> </ul> <p>#zip</p> ]]>
