rally competent care</p> <li> <p>Excellent communication skills and a collaborative spirit</p> <li> <p>Comfort using electronic health records and data tools</p> <li> <p>3 years’ experience in outpatient or urgent care preferred</p> <li> <p>Spanish/English bilingual skills strongly preferred</p> </ul> <hr> <p><strong>Compensation & Perks:</strong></p> <ul> <li> <p>NHSC Loan Repayment Program eligibility</p> <li> <p>Competitive salary + productivity bonus</p> <li> <p>Paid malpractice and CME</p> <li> <p>Health, dental, and vision insurance</p> <li> <p>401(k) with up to 4% employer match</p> <li> <p>Generous PTO and 9 paid holidays</p> <li> <p>Employer-paid life, short-term, and long-term disability insurance</p> <li> <p>Employee Assistance Program</p> <li> <p>Paid leave options for bereavement, maternity, military, and more</p> </ul> <p>#zip</p> ]]>
