d support workflow optimization</p> <li> <p>Ensure compliance with safety, quality, and regulatory requirements</p> </ul> <h4>Qualifications</h4> <ul> <li> <p>Bachelor’s degree or equivalent experience</p> <li> <p>Prior experience in aerospace manufacturing</p> <li> <p>Strong background in indirect or raw material purchasing</p> <li> <p>Solid understanding of manufacturing processes and supply chain operations</p> <li> <p>Proven negotiation and supplier relationship management skills</p> <li> <p>Strong analytical, organizational, and communication skills</p> <li> <p>ERP system experience and proficiency in Microsoft Office</p> <li> <p>Ability to work independently in a fast-paced environment</p> </ul> <h4>Work Environment</h4> <ul> <li> <p>Manufacturing setting with regular interaction on the production floor</p> <li> <p>Exposure to noise, machinery, and industrial conditions; PPE required when applicable</p> <li> <p>Occasional travel between local facilities</p> </ul> <p><span>#toponehire</span></p> ]]>
