nt strongly preferred</p> <li> <p>Solid understanding of standard costing and variance analysis</p> <li> <p>ERP system experience and strong Excel skills</p> <li> <p>Strong analytical, communication, and collaboration skills</p> <li> <p>Ability to manage multiple priorities in a fast-paced, cross-functional environment</p> <li> <p>Professional, team-oriented mindset</p> </ul> <h4><strong>Work Environment</strong></h4> <ul> <li> <p>Office-based role with regular interaction on the manufacturing floor</p> <li> <p>Requires ability to work at a computer for extended periods and occasional standing/walking in production areas</p> </ul> <p>#toponehire</p> ]]>
