sive accounting experience in a complex manufacturing environment</p> <li> <p>Proven experience leading and developing accounting teams</p> <li> <p>Experience supporting multi-entity, multi-currency operations</p> <li> <p>Strong systems and ERP experience </p> <li> <p>Excellent analytical, communication, and leadership skills</p> </ul> <hr> <h3>Compensation & Benefits</h3> <ul> <li> <p>Competitive base salary: $190,000 – $210,000</p> <li> <p>Annual performance bonus target of approximately 25%</p> <li> <p>Sign-on bonus negotiable</p> <li> <p>Comprehensive medical, dental, and vision benefits</p> <li> <p>Company-sponsored retirement program</p> <li> <p>Above-market PTO and paid holidays</p> <li> <p>Long-term career growth and leadership development opportunities</p> </ul> <hr> <h3>Additional Information</h3> <p>This role is being handled with discretion. Company details will be shared during the interview process.</p> <p>Equal Opportunity Employer. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to protected characteristics.</p> <p> </p> <p><span>#toponehire</span></p> ]]>
