referred. <li>3+ years of experience in CRM administration or technology support. <li>Strong problem-solving skills and ability to manage multiple priorities. <li>Excellent communication and training skills. <li>Familiarity with financial services technology (Addepar, custodial platforms) is a plus. <li>Proficiency in using AI tools such as Microsoft Co-Pilot, ChatGPT, and Gemini is desirable. <li>Familiarity with AI automation using Python, Claude Code, and/or Gemini CLI is a plus <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office Suite; experience with workflow automation tools is desirable. </ul> <p>#toponehire</p> ]]>
