<span><span>BSBA in accounting </span></span> <li><span><span>CPA certification required </span></span> <li><span><span>Minimum 7-10 years of experience in public accounting </span></span> <li><span><span>Ability to meet deadlines and work on multiple client projects </span></span> <li><span><span>Excellent written and verbal communication skills </span></span> <li><span><span>Organized and detail oriented </span></span> <li><span><span>Working knowledge of accounting and auditing principles </span></span> <li><span><span>Experience with QuickBooks, Microsoft Word and Excel, ProSystem fx Tax </span></span> </ul> <p> <span><span>Members of the firm enjoy monthly gatherings, an annual holiday party, annual end of tax season party, and summer outing. The firm is committed to giving back to the community, with at least one philanthropic effort per quarter. They also have their own charitable foundation, through which they award scholarships to local accounting students and host their annual Kickball and Wiffleball tournaments each summer!</span></span></p> <p>#toponehire</p> <p> </p> ]]>
