d vendors to obtain competitive bids and select reliable service providers.</span></span></span> <li><span><span><span>Maintain comprehensive records of maintenance activities, expenses, and warranties.</span></span></span> </ul> <p> <span><span><span>Regulatory Compliance</span></span></span></p> <ul> <li><span><span><span>Ensure compliance with all applicable local, state, and federal housing regulations, including fair housing laws and low-income housing guidelines.</span></span></span> <li><span><span><span>Staying updated on regulatory changes and ensure the property’s policies and procedures align with the requirements.</span></span></span> <li><span><span><span>Assist with the preparation and submission of required reports, documentation, and certifications.</span></span></span> </ul> <p> <span><span><span>Lease Administration</span></span></span></p> <ul> <li><span><span><span>Oversee the lease application process, including screening prospective tenants, conducting background checks, and verifying income eligibility,</span></span></span> <li><span><span><span>Prepare and execute lease agreements, ensuring adherence to relevant regulations and policies.</span></span></span> <li><span><span><span>Enforce lease terms and policies, including addressing lease violations and initiating eviction processes when necessary.</span></span></span> </ul> <p> <span><span>Qualifications</p> <p> Previous experience in property management, specifically in Section 8 and LIHTC</span></span><br /> <span>#toponehire</span></p> ]]>
