y functions. <li>Ability to bend, pull, stoop and reach. <li>Ability to lift 25-30 lbs. <li>May be exposed to heat, fumes, noise, and humidity, etc. <li>Must have the cognitive and mental capacity to perform essential job functions. <li>Must be able to communicate effectively orally and in writing. <li>Visual acuity to read documents, computer screens, files, etc. </ul> <p><span>#toponehire</span></p> ]]>
